On Escalation Ticket # 00429904 the new comment has been added: Augustina Sidor:

Hi,


1. Is it possible to change the computer's name so that it is not the same?

2. If not, Enable Virtual Desktop Clones Support:

	 - 	Go to the System Configuration settings page.
	 - 	Enable the "Virtual Desktop Clones Support" setting.
	 - 	Test the system behavior.


3. If the above doesn't work, collect logs from the registration process:

	 - 	Enable debugging logs on the server:

	 - 	Edit the file /EPPServer/sieratool/webservicefree/webservice.php using a text editor (e.g., vim).
	 - 	Set the following values:

	 - 	set DEBUG_VERBOSITY to 1017
	 - 	set DEBUG to true


4. Re-register the affected macOS machines.

	 - 	Collect the logs from the following location:

	 - 	/EPPServer/sieratool/log/WebServiceFree.log
	 - 	Disable logging once logs are collected:


5. Revert the changes made to /EPPServer/sieratool/webservicefree/webservice.php to disable debugging.


6.Â Provide the collected logs for further analysis.


Regards,
Augustina


FYI @WaitingOnDevOps
